<h1>PvP Tournament</h1>
<p>In the coming weeks we will be hosting a PvP ladder-ranked tournament! Players will be faced off in 1v1 matches, three fights per match, the winner of each match moving up the ladder! The winner of the tournament will be given Rythir the Wizard's head.</p>
<p>Sign-ups close on <b>1st June 2013</b> and the tournament will be held on the <b>8th June 2013 at 23:00 GMT</b></p>
